Revision history for Virani

?.?.?  ?/?
       - add Virani->get_sets for getting a list of configured sets, exposed
         via mojo-virani as the get_sets=1 param and remotely fetchable via
         Virani::Client->get_sets or virani --list-sets
       - misc. minor cleanups
       - SECURITY: fix default allowed_subnets entry of '192.168.0.0/', which
         parsed as a /0 and matched any IP, to '192.168.0.0/16'
       - bpf2tshark: fix handling of '(', which was never matched, fix ether
         fields being emitted as etc.* instead of eth.*, and don't warn when
         the filter starts with and/or
       - fix cache file naming differing between get_cache_file with and
         without a file specified, causing needless cache misses
       - fix get_cache_file returning undef when auto_no_cache=0 and the
         cache dir is usable
       - fix sets ref check in new checking allowed_subnets instead
       - new_from_conf now reports TOML parse errors properly
       - filter_clean now trims whitespace before the leading '-' check so
         ' -foo' can't slip through
       - bless into the passed class so subclassing works
       - get_pcap_local sets path to undef if the output file was never
         generated and skips the copy
       - dedup option validation between get_cache_file and get_pcap_local
       - cache the Net::Subnet matcher instead of rebuilding it per call
       - remove the unused default_max_time config var
       - require perl 5.10 as named captures are used
       - misc POD fixes, =head1 to =head2 for the check_* methods

1.2.0  2024-10-21/10:#0
       - misc POD cleanup
       - mojo-virani returns 418 now for pcap generation errors

1.1.0  2023-08-12/22:00
       - add ts_is_unixtime and pcap_glob config vars
       - get the set earlier if need for default for get_pcap_local
       - bump depend of File::Find::IncludesTimeRange to 0.2.0
       - misc doc updates

1.0.1  2023-08-07/11:30
       - bpf translate fix for src/dst with out host
       - properly reads type from config
       - log/display padded time
       - display/log BPF translation

0.3.0  2023-08-03/15:45
        - add req_start, req_start_s, req_end, req_end_s, and req_time keys to metadata
        - fix padding handling

0.2.0  2023-08-03/08:45
        - mojo-virani sets content type to application/x-download
        - misc verbosity fixes/cleanup
        - remove needlessly copying the cache file
        - fix typo in name used for syslog messages
        - add etime/stime aliases for start/end args for mojo-virani
        - add --buffer to virani
        - enable special for Time::Piece::Guess
        - misc doc cleanups/updates

0.1.1  2023-07-31/17:30
        - Fix the handling when filter is undef.
        - Minor doc updates.

0.1.0  2023-07-31/12:00
        - Add timestamp logging for when getting a PCAP
        - Support using ARGV for filter info
        - Support reading filter from a file

0.0.1  2023-03-14/13:30
        - Initial release.

